    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a number of children with psychiatric problems as young as six years old, and I had felt that they should not be with adults.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think some were abused by some of the adult men in the units.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I had established a children's unit there, and I had written about that and had it published in a professional magazine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had written some articles here on health in occupational therapy journals, even in the last, well, 10 years or so.",
      "word_count": 22
